README
======

menutag
-------

This provides a ``{% menu %}`` template tag.

**Dependencies**

``import lxml``

**Usage**

::

  {% menu active="contact" active_class="active" %}
    <a href="" link="home">Homepage</a>
    <a href="" link="about_us">About us</a>
    <a href="" link="contact">Contact</a>
  {% endmenu %}

The ``link`` attributes will be removed and the Contact link will be given the
``active`` class.

Available options are::

  active            Specify the active link.
  active_class      Give the active link this class.
  active_id         Give the active link this id.
  link_class        Give all link this class.
